The paper deals with a generalized theory of evidence that combines probability theory and fuzzy set theory to deal with uncertain information in AI systems. This makes it likely to belong to the sub-categories of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Machine Learning (cs.LG), Data Mining (cs.DM), Social and Information Networks (cs.SI), and Information Theory (cs.IT).
